4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course provides individuals with the opportunity to start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models. The course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field. It is a 16-week program that prepares participants to enter high-paying tech fields. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and statistics. Participants will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. They will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course includes real-life case studies and hands-on experience with industry-standard tools. The instructors for the course are experienced professionals in the field of AI and machine learning. The course is taught in English or Spanish, and live classes are taught in the language of the participant's campus. Participants will receive a certificate upon completion of the course. For more information, visit the website: "https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning". stop